      "en": "Convert argument strings to objects and assign them as attributes of the namespace. Return the populated namespace. Previous calls to add_argument() determine exactly what objects are created and how they are assigned. See the documentation for add_argument() for details. args - List of strings to parse. The default is taken from sys.argv. namespace - An object to take the attributes. The default is a new empty Namespace object."
